During Ansible phase:
---------------------
After changing encoding of system to UTF-8 (if you get error in jenkins) - Later restart it

Send SSH key from user 'jenkins' to 'ansible_user' in the client machine
Ex : simha>>su jenkins
     jenkins>>ssh-keygen
     jenkins>>ssh-copy-id simha@127.0.0.1
     jenkins>>ssh-copy-id <userofcontainer>@<ipaddrofContainer>
     // for multiple devices